<i>♪ On a hill ♪</i>

41:30.196 --> 41:31.614
<i>♪ Far away ♪</i>

41:32.490 --> 41:35.743
<i>♪ Stood an old rugged cross ♪</i>

41:36.660 --> 41:38.078
<i>♪ The emblem ♪</i>

41:38.662 --> 41:39.830
<i>♪ Of suffering ♪</i>

41:39.914 --> 41:41.081
[intense music swells]

41:48.339 --> 41:50.466
